{"tid":1983493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"世界衛生組織1台載著武漢肺疑似感染者的檢體車輛在緬甸若開邦遭到襲擊，車輛駕駛身亡","createTime":"2020-04-22T01:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T01:57:08.000Z","uid":66260,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fde958dc08b81e2c17feebb6d2df434404919a16","tid":1983493,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:01:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=1518485678326722&amp;set=a.162942763881027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D1518485678326722%26set%3Da.162942763881027&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=c3915a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=1518485678326722&amp;set=a.162942763881027</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合國今天(21日)表示，隸屬於世界衛生組織(WHO)的1台車輛在緬甸若開邦(Rakhine)遭到襲擊，車輛駕駛身亡。這台車輛載著俗稱武漢肺炎的2019年冠狀病毒疾病(COVID-19)疑似感染者的檢體，準備送到檢驗所進行化驗，以確定採檢者是否感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n聯合國駐緬甸辦公室在臉書貼文，對這起世衛組織車輛遇襲事件表達「極度悲傷」，並證實車輛駕駛佩松溫貌(Pyae Song Win Maung，音譯)已在若開邦的敏比亞(Minbya)一場襲擊中遇害身亡。<br />\n聯合國駐緬甸辦公室的臉書貼文表示：「這名身亡的世衛組織員工駕著車身貼有明顯聯合國標誌的車輛，從若開邦(Rakhine)首府實兌(Sittwe)開往仰光(Yangon)，車上載著檢體樣本前往緬甸衛生暨體育部(Ministry of Health and Sports)的檢驗所。」"},{"pid":"255b35d3030d5d27076a28c3c26c49d8eed1284d","tid":1983493,"uid":181801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:30:44.000Z","msg":"真勇武"},{"pid":"79f6f297f3ae4c89f45deef22a46269d969956cc","tid":1983493,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:31:37.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526aaa4ac73ed38faa092d5089032de09fe15645","tid":1983493,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:33:51.000Z","msg":"緬甸親支㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90f02b02ad235ac